data.name: WrongJavaVersionException
desc: indicates that an operation involving Java (probably executing Java code) failed due to a wrong Java version.

properties.name: DetectedVersion
desc: contains the Java version that has been detected, or is left empty if this is unknown.

properties.name: HighestSupportedVersion
desc: contains the highest Java version for which the operation would succeed, or is left empty if this is unknown.

properties.name: LowestSupportedVersion
desc: contains the lowest Java version for which the operation would succeed, or is left empty if this is unknown.
